\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T07:36:10.000Z","msg":"寫咩文親咩人我有保留<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">但你唔識寫中文就死返5p<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"befd0725ce4c94b8f74b490a4d9687ffcf8d866b","tid":1088932,"uid":203783,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T08:03:47.000Z","msg":"為咗寫快啲字我試過唔寫正體中文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n例如「關」寫做「関」<br />\n有同學癲到「廣東」寫做「広東」，「身邊」寫做「身辺」<br />\n<br />\n用和制漢字雖然過到自己心裡面果關，同埋真係快咗少少，但慳得一筆得一筆好容易培養到惰性，第時想再懶啲就會寫咗殘體<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申冇寫過殘體，出嚟做嘢已經全面使用正體中文。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d9185a28ea8f88336832ed6bf5e0c9b972ab828","tid":1088932,"uid":69753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e32d04bee582b850623b9c9a00b49d71504d3ed","tid":1088932,"uid":210662,"like":10,"dislike":8,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T07:12:16.000Z","msg":"吾好撚傻啦<br />\n寫下簡體就話係大陸仔<br />\n咁我寫下英文又變鬼佬呀<br />\n寫下日文又變架仔呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T09:06:58.000Z","msg":"吾系牙...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5cc8dba801db42f5c4fc3049924e9c16215d876","tid":1088932,"uid":44954,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T09:17:26.000Z","msg":"其實快幾多？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />利申少少分數唔值得我放棄自己嘅原則<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再利申唔洗考"},{"pid":"23ecdb484715ea5d0230982e5c1768af5e9884fe","tid":1088932,"uid":19005,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T09:18:41.000Z","msg":"邊忽快呀<br />\n寫開繁體咪咁